work-overlay/
=============
Staging area for Phase 2 — files to be moved into the work dotfiles repo
(jerry-feng-skydio/dotfiles).

Files to copy into work repo root:
  .bashrc_local         → ~/.bashrc_local (work-specific bash config)
  .vimrc_local          → ~/.vimrc_local  (vim-lcm rtp, work vim settings)
  .vimrc_plugins_local  → ~/.vimrc_plugins_local (djinni/kotlin/swift/AnsiEsc)
  .gitconfig_local      → ~/.gitconfig_local (work git identity)
  setup.sh              → replaces existing work setup.sh

Files to remove from work repo root after copying in:
  .bashrc
  .vimrc
  .tmux.conf
  .gitconfig
  .inputrc
  coc-settings.json

Git commands to run in work repo:
  git submodule add https://github.com/jfeng94/dotfiles personal
  git rm --cached .bashrc .vimrc .tmux.conf .gitconfig .inputrc coc-settings.json
  rm .bashrc .vimrc .tmux.conf .gitconfig .inputrc coc-settings.json
  # copy in the files from this directory
  git add .
  git commit -m "refactor: delegate to personal dotfiles submodule"
